description: Yami reflects on the time he spent working alongside William Vangeance, captain of the Golden Dawn, and the secret mission they were given. Can the two strong-willed mages work together to make the Wizard King proud?
title: Yami and Vangeance

description: It's time to see who will make up the Royal Knights! Led by Mereoleona, this squad will take on the Eye of the Midnight Sun and protect the kingdom. But who is the fourth Black Bulls member that is joining Asta, Luck, and Noelle?
title: Formation of the Royal Knights

description: The Black Bulls learn why their home base keeps changing shape; that same power is put to the test against members of the Eye of the Midnight Sun.
title: Crazy Magic Battle

description: Fierce fighter Mereoleona takes on Rhya of the Third Eye and his wide range of formidable Copy Magic spells as Zora tries to figure out how they work.
title: Mereoleona vs. Ryha the Disloyal

description: It's a battle for the ages as the Clover Kingdom's mightiest mage takes on the dynamic leader of the Eye of the Midnight Sun, and an unexpected guest.

description: Royal Knights and disgraced mages alike encounter friends and squad mates whose bodies have been taken over by reincarnated elves. Can Black Asta help?
title: Overwhelming Disadvantage

description: Mereoleona is left to face five powerful elf enemies alone, putting her "undefeated" title to the test. Mimosa's Royal Knight teammates turn on her.
title: The Desperate Path Toward Survival

description: While everyone is clashing at the decoration ceremony—the capital is under attack! Hordes of undead fill the streets, and it's up to the Magic Knights to defend the kingdom. Will they have the power to stop the wrath of a madman?
title: Capital Riot

description: Gauche rushes off with Marie, leaving Asta and Sister Theresa to fight Sally and her Earth monster. But, after an encouraging peptalk, Gauche reconsiders his methods and teams up with Asta for a powerful new spell!
title: To Help Somebody Someday

description: After Gauche successfully blocks Licht's attack, the Black Bulls wait for Finral's magic to recover so they can head back. As they wait with their new captives three new enemies appear! Can the Magic Knights face the power of the Third Eye?
title: Three Eyes

description: The Black Bulls hit the beach for their next mission! But that doesn't mean they're on vacation—this is an important task from the Wizard King. To enter the Underwater Temple, they can only count on one person—Noelle!
title: A Black Beach Story

description: Up against three of the Eight Shining Generals, Yuno and the Golden Dawn prove the Clover Kingdom will not go down easily! But nothing compares to the magic used by the captain of the Golden Dawn, William Vangeance!
title: Whoever's Strongest Wins

description: Before he began his Magic Knight journey, Asta met a strange man named Fanzell, who has issues keeping his clothes on! Zell certainly knows his way around a sword, though, so he takes Asta on as his student.
title: The Man Named Fanzell

description: As Fanzell continues his search for Domina, he has an unfortunate run-in with the rest of the Black Bulls. After settling the misunderstanding, they're happy to send him on his way…that is, until the base is attacked!
title: The Man Named Fanzell, Continued

description: Though the Queen is terrifying, she's the least of their worries when both the Third Eye and the Diamond Kingdom attack the Witches' Forest! Offering to help protect the forest, they make a deal with the Queen to heal Asta's arms.
title: The Battlefield Decision

description: The battle heats up as Asta and the Black Bulls face the furious flamed-up Fana! But when her fire gets too hot and starts affecting Vanessa and Finral's magic, it's up to Noelle to use her water magic to cool things off!
title: Flames of Hatred

description: An unexpected reunion could lead to turnaround in this heated battle! Asta and Mars fight side-by-side to go up against Fana and the powerful Salamander.
title: The Promised World

description: It's study session time! Klaus wants his team ready to face the Eye of the Midnight Sun at any given moment. So what better way to prep than studying everything their enemy has done?

input: The Secret of the Eye of the Midnight Sun
Secret of the Eye of the Midnight Sun

title: The Secret of the Eye of the Midnight Sun

description: Things at the star festival are starting to heat up. Jack, of the Green Praying Mantis', challenges Yami to a deadly battle of selling the most food! Who will make it to the end of the festival?

input: Battle to the Death?! Yami vs. Jack
to the Death?! Yami vs. Jack

title: Battle to the Death?! Yami vs. Jack

description: The Captain of the Blue Rose Knights is ready to show her thorns when she starts attracting the wrong kind of attention at the festival.
title: The Briar Maiden's Melancholy

description: Without any mana, there's no way Asta can make it to the top of this volcano! That is, unless he can control his secret power. When everyone finally makes it to the top, that can only mean one thing—time for a soak!
title: Saint Elmo's Fire

description: Asta is fired up for their first match, but Xerx seems more interested in a nap! Looks like it's up to just Asta and Mimosa to carry the team. Luckily, Mimosa is bringing some brand-new skills to the fight!
title: Flower of Resolution

description: Rill surprises everyone by entering the competition! Are the knights ready to face a Magic Knight captain? Or will Rill make everyone question a captain's capabilities? Meanwhile, Luck and Klaus get ready to start their first match.
title: Mage X

description: It's a battle between brothers as Finral and Langris face off! But a dark power lies in Langris that could quickly turn the battle.

input: Special Little Brother vs. Failed Big Brother
Little Brother vs. Failed Big Brother

title: Special Little Brother vs. Failed Big Brother

description: While things are heating up in the tournament, Charmy is having her own dangerous encounter! Well, in her dreams at least. Get ready for an episode filled with charm…y, la!

input: Clover Clips: The Nightmarish Charmy Special!

title: Clover Clips: The Nightmarish Charmy Special!

description: Yami and Finral take on possessed members of the Golden Dawn. Noelle and Nozel must defend their siblings when the Silva family home is under siege.
title: The Battle for Clover Castle

description: Vanessa leads a group of Black Bulls trapped in a deadly dream world while Sally runs some quick experiments. Henry is determined to save his friends.
title: The Eyes in the Mirror

description: A team of squad captains and talented Magic Knights invade the Shadow Palace, where a few formidable elves await the arrival of the final magic stone.
title: Storming the Shadow Palace

description: Nozel's Mercury spells are the perfect match for Patry's Light Magic, but Asta's plan to drive the elf out of Vangeance's body doesn't go as expected.
title: The Ultimate Natural Enemy

description: As Yami and the elvish Charlotte test the limits of the devil's mighty Word Soul Magic, Nero asks Finral a favor and reveals a centuries-old secret.
title: Breaking the Seal

description: A flashback to the truth behind the first Wizard King's battle against the demon serves as prelude for a new face joining the fight against the devil.

input: A Reunion Across Time and Space

title: A Reunion Across Time and Space

description: The fight is not yet over: the kingdom is still rife with elves bent on revenge. Patry looks within for a solution--then it's time to bid farewell.
title: Dawn

description: Foes turned allies, knights, captains, and rivals alike push past their limits, finding new abilities as the epic devil battle reaches a fever pitch.
title: The Final Attack

description: Yami is agog at what--or who--has taken the place of Julius's body. Asta and Secre are called before the Magic Parliament for their devilish dealings.
title: Three Problems

description: Asta's Black Asta form does him no favors in the court of Damnatio Kira. It's up to a powerful few to save Asta's head from the chopping block.

input: As Pitch Black as It Gets

title: As Pitch Black as It Gets

description: Secre reminisces about the first Wizard King, his friendship with the elf Licht, the devil's machinations, and how it all came to a heartbreaking end.
title: Nero Reminisces... Part One

description: Secre reflects on Patry's reincarnation and that of his fellow elves, the utter havoc they wreaked, how it all ended, and what her future might hold.
title: Nero Reminisces... Part Two

description: The Black Bulls return to a hideout in dire need of rebuilding, but first they must track down Yami's escaped beasts, now likely feral--and hungry.
title: Return

description: Yami's visit to the Blue Rose Knights' HQ couldn't come at a worse time for Charlotte, who can no longer hide her feelings for her fellow captain.
title: The Blue Rose's Confession

description: An expedition to the Heart Kingdom uncovers a beautiful, mana-rich land that is a little less than welcoming. Finral resolves to turn over a new leaf.
title: To the Heart Kingdom!

description: A contingent of Black Bulls seeks info from Gordon's family of Curse Magic experts, while Noelle digs deeper into what really killed her mother Acier.
title: Clues

description: The devil Megicula is in the Spade Kingdom! Princess Lolopechka of the Heart Kingdom reveals what it will take to defeat him and lays out a deadline.
title: The Devil Megicula

description: The trainees split into teams hoping to find a certain magic item in the Yultim dungeon--if the gigantic spider lurking there doesn’t find them first.
title: The Lion Awakens, Continued

description: Mereoleona grabs a few fiery handsful of Black Bulls to join her squad in a training session at Yultim Volcano, where several surprises await them.
title: The Lion Awakens

description: Asta, Yuno, Noelle, and Secre are dispatched to Hage Village, where Sister Lily presses the quartet into service at the village's newest institution.
title: A New Resolve

description: The Wizard King summons the Magic Knight captains to brief them on the alliance with the Heart Kingdom against Megicula and to plan their next steps.

input: The New Magic Knight Squad Captains' Meeting
New Magic Knight Squad Captains' Meeting

title: The New Magic Knight Squad Captains' Meeting

description: Asta and Noelle arrive at the Fuegoleon residence for a secretive gathering, unreasonable requests, and an all-out brawl between two heavy hitters.
title: Those Who Have Been Gathered

description: Finral asks Asta to help him break his own curse: his flirty nature. Blue Rose Knights and Black Bulls come together for a meeting--or is it a mixer?

description: The Black Bulls are (mostly) training in Raquey when Kahono and Kiato approach them for help defending an Underwater Temple that's under attack.
